## Limitations
The estimates provided are based on varying methodologies and assumptions, which can lead to significant discrepancies. Additionally, the figures do not account for unforeseen global events such as pandemics or economic crises that can exacerbate hunger. The complexity of implementing global solutions and the need for sustained political and financial commitment also pose challenges to accurately predicting the cost to end world hunger.